2149
00:53:49,730 --> 00:53:54,170
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(A foul smell hits their noses.)</font>

2150
00:53:50,530 --> 00:53:52,070
<font size="64">- Why do I smell manure? - Something smells off.</font>

2151
00:53:52,070 --> 00:53:53,270
<font size="64">All right, guys.</font>

2152
00:53:53,270 --> 00:53:55,140
<font size="64">- You smell something, right? - Yes.</font>

2153
00:53:55,340 --> 00:53:56,540
<font size="64">- I smell squid. - Yes.</font>

2154
00:53:56,540 --> 00:53:59,540
<font size="64">This is the last mission that will bring you...</font>

2155
00:53:57,010 --> 00:54:00,840
