<font size="64">The other teams will play defense.</font>

2199
00:55:30,900 --> 00:55:32,270
<font size="64">- Okay. - Okay.</font>

2200
00:55:32,170 --> 00:55:34,340
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(We'll play offense first!)</font>

2201
00:55:32,270 --> 00:55:33,740
<font size="64">- We'll play offense. - Okay.</font>

